response.overview: Drop into the cockpit alongside the world's greatest fighter pilots as they take many of the United States military's most fearsome modern-day fighter jets out for a series of death-defying test flights. Experience the power, speed and maneuverability of cutting-edge fighting machines such as of the F-16 Fighting Falcon, F-117A Stealth, F-22 Raptor and the JSF with this collection of breathtaking aerial footage highlights.
response.title: Jets: Vol. 3: Fury
